> pml4, pgd, pmd, pte  (kernel names)
> PML4E, PDPE, PDE, PTE   (AMD hardware names)
No actually a PML4E is a PML4 _E_ntry in the AMD/Intel docs.
PML4 is the official name for the fourth level page.
